1270
01:01:35,917 --> 01:01:38,959
♪ Where your crazy heart ♪

1271
01:01:39,041 --> 01:01:40,792
♪ ♪

1272
01:01:40,875 --> 01:01:43,792
♪ Wants to go ♪

1273
01:01:43,875 --> 01:01:48,458
♪ ♪

1274
01:01:48,542 --> 01:01:51,500
♪ Love's a baby
